<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{مَا مَنَعَكَ أَلَّا تَسْجُدَ إِذْ أَمرتك}</span> الْآيَةَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ محمدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(أَلَّا تَسْجُدَ)</span> مَعْنَاهُ: أَن تسْجد، و <span class="c2">(لَا)</span> مُؤَكدَة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>